title: Touring an Old West Movie Set (Premium)
description:
This is a preview episode. Get the full episode, and many more, ad free, on our supporter's feed: https://getsleepy.com/support.


Touring an Old West Movie Set
Tonight, we’ll travel to a vast and wild desert in the southwestern United States and tour a fictional town, which is actually a film set. Its rustic buildings and tattered storefronts serve as the backdrop for movies about the Old West. 😴 

Sound design: desert ambiance, horse trotting. 🏜🐴
Narrator: TK Kellman
